; Regression test for issue #870: Cannot use --dc with --collapse or -X (BZ#870)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/870
; Using --dc with --collapse on the register command causes a crash:
; "Cannot compare an amount to a sequence"

2024/01/01 Salary
    Income:Salary    $-1000.00
    Assets:Checking   $1000.00

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food     $200.00
    Assets:Checking  $-200.00

test reg --dc --collapse -> 1
__ERROR__
While comparing if 0 is less than ($1000.00, $-1000.00):
While handling posting from "$FILE", line 11:
>     Expenses:Food     $200.00
Error: Cannot compare an amount to a sequence
end test
